Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: This St. Albert distribution building offers 149,207 sq. ft. on ±11.75 acres with a 6.05 acre graveled and compacted storage yard and potential for rail loading. Great location in St. Albert, taking advantage of lower property taxes, only 1.25 km to Anthony Henday ring road and with public transit in front of the building. Featuring dock and grade level loading and recent updates including the recently painted exterior and warehouse interior painted white.
